title: Power Play by Danielle Steel
description:
Someone I know requested this personally. When I tried to find it on Mobilism all the links were dead due to takedown notices.

The only torrent I found was on Kickass and even THAT was removed due to take down notice.

This pissed me off. Hence this release.

Not like the bitch can't afford to feed her kids having sold over 800 million books.

I'd rather rip my eyes out than read it, but to each their own, I wanted this out there. 

It's epub and mobi converted from Amazon retail awz that was deDRM'd


___
